Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对于我来说  她更像是个小妹妹\NShe's more like a little sister to me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你不介意我试一试吧\NSo you don't mind if I take a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}尽可一试  首长\NShe's all yours, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}续杯\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThanks.
