Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定吗\NAnd you're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确定吗\NYou sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那好  你先跟紧  等我消息\NOkay. Great. Just, uh, just hang tight till you hear from me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是谁\NWho is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  听着  我让你跟紧就好\NNo, listen to me. I said hang tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们得走了\NWe got to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能让我先吃完汉堡吗\NCan I at least finish my burger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人被吸血鬼杀死了  迪恩\NWe got a vamp kill, Dean --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在路易斯安那州的卡伦科\NCarencro, Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好久没都吃过蔬菜海鲜辣炖汤了\NIt's been a while since I've had some étouffée.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁提供的线索\NWho's the source?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马丁・奎恩\NMartin Creaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉  刚刚有那么一瞬\NSorry -- for a minute there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以为你说的是马丁・奎恩\NI thought you said Martin Creaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}疯人院的疯狂马丁\NCrazy Martin from the loony bin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上个月他在格伦代尔泉医院获释了\NGlendale Springs discharged him last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后呢\NAnd?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}难道他不应该在保护病房拼玩具玩吗\NShouldn't he be assembling toys in a padded room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他怎么又重操旧业了\NWhat's he doing back on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我请他这么做的\NI asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么\NYou what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他出来的时候给我打了电话\NLook, he called me when he got out, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问我有没有办法\Nasked if I had anything for him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帮助他重新开始猎魔\Nthat might help him ease back into the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他似乎康复了  基本康复了\NHe seemed okay -- mostly --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我答应帮他\Nso I said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这几周我都让他盯着本尼\NI've had him tracking Benny for the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你让"基本康复"的马丁去盯着本尼\NYou put "mostly okay" Martin on Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"基本康复"的人猎魔都做些啥\NWhat is "mostly okay" doing hunting at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是猎魔  迪恩  是跟踪\NNot hunting, Dean -- tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只是观察报告  我交代得十分清楚\NObserve and report only. I was crystal clear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真不敢相信\NWow. I can't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗  迪恩  你不敢相信\NReally, Dean? You don't believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为本尼是个吸血鬼\NBecause Benny's a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而一个称职的猎人\NAnd any hunter worth his salt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不该让吸血鬼在外自由游荡\Nisn't gonna let one just walk around freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我让马丁监视他\NSo I had Martin keep tabs on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在看来我的决定是正确的\NAnd right now, it's looking like I made the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马丁说这事是本尼做的\NSo Martin's saying Benny did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"好吧"\N"Okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果本尼在路易斯安那吸干人血\NIf Benny's in Louisiana draining folks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们该去查查看\Nwe should look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}欢迎来到路易斯安那
