Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说在找"火山爆发"[也可译作长牙]\NYou said "look for an eruption."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看维苏威火山\NHow's Mount Vesuvius?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我大概一周前到的镇上\NI got into town about a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}昨晚之前一无所获  他没有行动\NUp until last night, nothing. He's been clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他在干什么\NDoing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干他自己的活儿\NJust minding his own business.
