Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼在小酒馆里打工\NBenny's working at the gumbo shack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对  端盘子  倒咖啡  什么活都干\NYeah. Slinging hash, pouring coffee -- the whole bit.
