Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是这里的人叫他罗伊\NFolks around here call him Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马丁  你确定自己没事吗\NMartin, you sure you're running on a full charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事\NY-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早上用一下休克疗法\NL-little s-shock therapy in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就活蹦乱跳了\Nand I-I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说说昨晚发生什么事\NTell us what happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我像往常一样跟踪他回家\NSo, I followed him home, just like every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他拐上一条小路\NHe turned up a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听到一声尖叫\NI hear a scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟过去一看\NI catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一具尸体\NBoom -- there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}酒馆里罗伊打量的那个傻瓜  被吸干了\NThe old coot that Roy was eyeballing at the joint -- vamped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等...你到底有没有亲眼看到本尼杀人\NWait -- did you actually see Benny kill the guy or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到的够多了\NI saw enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你没亲眼看到他动手\NWell, then, how can you be sure it was Benny
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么能确定是本尼干的\Nif you didn't actually see him do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我看到本尼拐上那条小路\NB-b-because I saw Benny turn up the path,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}两秒钟之后\Nand then two seconds later,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就被一具喉咙被撕开的尸体绊倒了\NI trip over a body with its throat ripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有没有听说过奥卡姆剃刀\NLook, man, you ever hear of Occam's Razor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}14世纪英国奥坎逻辑学家威廉提出的原理  即"如无必要  勿增实体"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"简单的才是真相"  没那么复杂\N"Keep it simple, stupid?" it's not that complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这中间有很多漏洞  马丁\NThere's a lot of holes, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}漏洞  我们现在要关注的\NHoles?! The only holes we should be looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是被害者脖子上的洞\Nare in the vic's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这像你认识的本尼会做的事吗\NThis sound like the Benny you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不认得本尼\NI don't know Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你认识本尼\NThe Benny you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说什么呢\NSay what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我为什么有一种\NWhy am I getting the distinct impression
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你哥哥在担保一个吸血鬼清白的感觉\Nthat your brother is vouching for a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计们  不要吵\NGuys, let's not argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没人在吵  但是如果是本尼\NNobody's arguing, but if this is Benny --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在只是假设\Nand that's a big "If" --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是他\NOh, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟他有交情  知道吗\NI got history with the guy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会问都不问就下手的\NI'm not signing up for a witch hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我欠他的情不止这些\NI owe him more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}全能的上帝啊\NWhat in God's great creation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}温彻斯特家的人怎么会欠吸血鬼的情\Ncould a Winchester possibly owe a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有听错吧\NAm I hearing this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  查明真相之前\NLook, until we get the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们先收起嗜血冲动  把这件事做好\Nwe stow the bloodlust and we work this case right,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不然我们分开行动\Nor we work it separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他脑袋搬家才是把事做好\NDoing it right would be separating his head from his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要时间  萨姆\NI just need some time, Sammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗  让尖牙鬼继续杀人  我看不行\NOh, yeah. Let the fang take another life? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你需要多久\NHow much time do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不是真的要听他的吧\NYou're not actually considering this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几小时足够了\NCouple hours, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果真的是本尼呢\NAnd what if it turns out to be Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果真是本尼  我自己处理\NThen it's Benny, and I'll deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几小时  迪恩  不能再多了\NCouple hours, Dean. No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我回头联系你\NI'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听我说\NH-hey. Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你开玩笑的吧\NYou're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他一走我们就行动\NWe're doing this as soon as he pulls away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  不行  马丁\NNo, we're not, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们得给他一点时间\NWe're gonna give him a little bit of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的哥哥  你说了算\NHey, it's your brother. It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还打算让他这样下去多久\NHow long are you gonna let him go on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真相就摆在他面前\NIt's staring him right in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有时候要看清真相很不容易\NWell, sometimes it's not easy to see things for what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}德克萨斯州  克米特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}捡球\NGet the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来\NCome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来\NCome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好样的\NGood job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想好见他要说什么了吗\NThought about what you're gonna say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想了又想  想来想去\NI've thought about it and thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我还是不知道\Nand I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}肯定有很多人告诉你正确的事情是\NLook, I'm sure you have a lot of people telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这里的一切\Nwhat the right thing to do is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆\NSam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是你的丈夫  艾米利亚\NHe's your husband, Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我不想\NBut I-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想去做正确的事\NI don't want to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说你和我在一起就是正确的事情\NI mean, this is the right thing, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许我会因为说这句话而下地狱\NAnd maybe I'm going to hell for saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我不想就此放弃\Nbut I'm not ready to give this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也不想\NNeither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你介意我花几天时间清醒一下头脑吗\NWould it bother you if I just took a few days to clear my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然可以\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}多长时间都行\NUh, take whatever time you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}实际上  我已经想好要什么了\NActually, I already know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我猜猜  秋葵汤饭\NLet me guess...gumbo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在我看到那些派之前是这么想的\NWas gonna be the gumbo till I saw pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}特色山核桃派\NWell, the special's pecan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然是了\NCourse it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就要那个\NLet's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}坏消息\NBad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们的山核桃派卖完了  我命该如此\NYou're out of pecan. Story of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事的  也许你可以补偿给我\NUh, that's all right. Maybe you can make it up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我事实上是来找一位老朋友的\NI'm actually looking for an old friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说他就在这附近  罗伊\NI heard he's kicking around these parts. His name's Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罗伊在这里上夜班\NWell, Roy works the night shift here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果我们说的是同一个罗伊的话\NI mean, if we're talking about the same Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他住在一个破旧的帐篷里\NUh, yeah, he, uh, putts around in a beat-up camper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看起来就像是恶魔禁地一样\NThing looks like a rolling deathtrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还以为只有我\NYeah, I thought I was the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}嘲笑他住的那一堆垃圾呢\Nwho gave him trouble over that piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你知不知道\NYou wouldn't happen to know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他这几天把帐篷搭在哪\Nwhere he's parking that thing these days, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他本来就把帐篷搭在后面\NWell, he, uh, was parking it out back,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但他刚打电话告诉我\Nbut just called to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说他要从公路去磨坊河几天\Nhe's gone up the road to Mill Creek for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他说为什么了吗\NUh, did he say why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想是去钓鱼\NOh... fishing, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他真的该休息一段了\NHe really deserves a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他近两周天天上双倍的班\NHe's been working doubles for the last two weeks straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样吧\NUm, listen, I, uh, I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他在我找到他之前过来了\NIf he pops up before I can find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}请你帮个忙让他给我打个电话\Nyou do me a favor and just have him give me a buzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者\NOr...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也可以直接打我\NCould just drop a dime yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然可以\NSure thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩\NDean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你叫\NAnd, uh, you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白  好的\NElizabeth. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我改天来吃派\NTake a rain check on that pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NDefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}古德瑞的法式餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}请在嘟一声后留言\NLeave a message at the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  我在卡伦科找到了一具\NBenny. I got a body here in Carencro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}脖子上被咬了两个洞的尸体\Nwith two holes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我又刚得知你去钓鱼了\NAnd I just found out you went fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}需要我告诉你这像发生了什么吗\NDo I need to tell you what this looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一条新留言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是我干的  迪恩\NIt's not me, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说的是哪个"我"\NNow, which "me" are we talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  还是罗伊\NBenny...or Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是想融入这一带\NI'm just trying to blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}融入\N"Blend in"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你刚把谁埋了\NWho'd you plant, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}二号遇害者\NVictim number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你想问我为什么不接电话\NIf you're concerned about the missed calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}原因是我不想把你牵扯进来\NI didn't want to get you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那么现在\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先放一放那事  谈一谈怎样\NWant to safety that thing, talk a little bit or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我洗耳恭听\NI'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是独居的吸血鬼干的\NRogue vamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}前几天晚上来到餐厅\NCame into the cafe a couple nights ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}名叫德斯蒙德的年轻人\NYoungster goes by the name of Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他想起了过去的好时光\NHe, uh, he remembers me from the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过去的好时光\NThe good old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道这很难相信\NI know it's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我不是一直都像现在这么可爱招人喜欢\NBut I haven't always been this cute and cuddly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他来和我叙叙旧  迪恩\NHe's chasing a memory, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}仅此而已\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他在组建新的巢穴\NHe's crewing up a new nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他希望我能带给他一点人气\NHe's hoping I can give him some cred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我拒绝了他\NI told him no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说到这一切都还好\NSo far, so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直接说那血案是怎么回事\NLet's get to the part about the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他想让我回心转意\NDidn't want to take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他想刺激我  丢下死尸\NHe's trying to roust me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到我变回来的自己  加入他\Nleaving dead bodies in my wake till I sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}两天两具尸体\NTwo bodies in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有人能把我赶出故乡  迪恩\NNo amateur is gonna kick me out of my hometown, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这次不行\NNot this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"故乡"\N"Hometown"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在这长大\NYou grew up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}土生土长\NBorn and bred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安德莉亚死后  你重出江湖\NWith Andrea gone and you hunting again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}似乎是时候到我回归故里了\Nseemed like the right time for a homecoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有你们兄弟才能让我服服帖帖\Nyou two being the only ones who keep all my ducks in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在一家餐厅重操旧业\NWent back to my old job at the cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我甚至找到一个我该负责的人\NI even found someone I hold myself accountable to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和我血肉相连的人  迪恩\NBest kind of someone, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}家人\NFamily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的曾孙女\NMy great-granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等  你没有\NNow, hold it, now. You didn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有\NUh, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她知道吗\NDoes she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  对她而言  我不过是一个过客\NNo, as far as she's concerned, I was just another drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我喜欢如此行事\NI'd like to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这里想过得舒服很艰难\NIt's been tough walking the line here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些年在炼狱里\Nafter all those years in purgatory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过惯了不缺食物的日子\Nnot having to deal with the hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是伊丽莎白\NBut Elizabeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我让我变得诚实\NShe keeps me honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我终于觉得是时候处理这件事情\NI finally feel like I got a handle on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}处理事情\NHandle on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  你手上有两具死尸\NBenny, you've got two stiffs on your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}两个猎人对你穷追不舍\Nand two hunters on your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托  是在餐厅找到我的笨蛋吗\NOh, please. The half-wit who found me at the cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我倒想陪他玩玩\NI'll take my chances with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个笨蛋是我弟弟派来的  相信我\NThat half-wit was sent by my brother, and trust me --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我弟弟绝对不是你想去招惹的人\Nmy brother's not someone you want to mess with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没时间陪他们玩  迪恩\NI don't have time to worry about them, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以前以为德斯蒙德不会惹祸上身\NI didn't think Desmond had an ounce of steel in his spine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我错了\Nbut I was wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以现在我要去做两天前就该做的事情\NSo now I'm gonna do what I should have done two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把他送到他该在的地方\Nwhich is put him back where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道解决此事只有一个办法  对吗\NYou know there's only one way to do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是让你袖手旁观\NAnd that is for you to sit on the sideline
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会说服萨姆和马丁跟踪德斯蒙德\Nwhile I convince Sam and Martin to go after Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他们见到你\NThey see you out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们不问青红皂白\Nthey don't care if you're gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会把你格杀勿论\Ncollecting for the march of dimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还没说话  他们就让你身首异处\NThey are gonna slice first and ask questions later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你明白的\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得他们会接手此事\NYou really think they'll go for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来解释清楚\NLet me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟踪那小子\NI follow your boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来到一条恐怖的小径\N...down a freaking path
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}被惨遭吸血鬼杀害的尸体绊倒\Nand trip over fresh vamp kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且你还亲眼所见\Nand then you practically catch him in the act
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他在掩埋另外一具尸体\Nof burying a second body
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还要偏袒他吗\Nand you're still taking his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吸血鬼会找郊区落单的人下手\NVampires pick people off from the outskirts of town, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不会舍近求远在他曾孙女\NNot in the cafe that they work in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上班的餐厅下手\Nwith their great-grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实  杀害人类不是他的行事风格\NIn fact, killing any human -- it's not his style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"不是他的行事风格"\N"Not his style"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"不是他的行事风格"\N"Not his style"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  我们来此调查一具死尸\NListen, Dean, we came here on a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你让我们给你点时间\NYou asked for some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在又发现一具尸体\Nand now there's another dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们还能相信你吗\NAre we just going on trust here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为死在我们手上的吸血鬼为数不少\NBecause we've killed for a lot less,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且你知道他们对我们恨之入骨\Nand you know how these things turn out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  我一清二楚\NYes, I do -- too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实  我经历的每一段关系\NIn fact, every relationship I have ever had
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在某种程度上都很糟糕\Nhas gone to crap at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我可以说唯独有本尼\NBut the one thing I can say about Benny --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他从没让我失望过\NHe has never let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}祝贺你  迪恩\NWell, good on you, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}经过这么多年你一定为终于找到\NMust feel great finally finding someone you can trust
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以信任的人而高兴\Nafter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只想说本尼是无辜的\NAll I'm saying is that Benny is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你感情用事\NYou're too close to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不会找到他\NYou're not gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你执意要做  我告诉你\NAnd if you do, I'm gonna tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能捡回性命算便宜你了\NYou'll be lucky to get out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你和他一起去  你也死期不远了\NAnd you -- you go with him, you're a dead man -- period.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想想那些无辜的生命  迪恩\NThese are innocent lives we're talking about, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还会为本尼的一片之词冒险吗\NAnd you're willing to risk that on Benny's word alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我当然会\NDamn right I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是干什么\NWhat...was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩做了选择\NDean made his choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们去忙正经事吧\NLet's go do our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}幸好你爸刚才没听到那些\NGlad your dad wasn't around to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他会想把你们俩\NHe'd have a mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从柴棚里揪出来  告诉你们那是什么\Nto take you both out the woodshed and show you what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也想亲自这么做\NHalf inclined to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你给我听着\NYou listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我能带你来\NI brought you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也能轻松地把你丢出去\NI can bring you out just as easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你想做的唯一一件事\NSo the only thing you're gonna be inclined to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是闭好嘴跟着我\Nis shut up and follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧  你说了算\NOkay. You say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说  哥哥选择相信吸血鬼而不是弟弟\NJust saying-- brother chooses a vampire over a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道我会是什么感受\NI know how I'd feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是萨姆  对吧\NYou are Sam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别紧张\NRelax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是来这打架的\NI ain't here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说了发生在你身上的事\NI heard about what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真不公平\NRough deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你这么说\NYeah, well, I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在我们陷入难题了  不是吗\NWe got ourselves a situation here now, though, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想是的\NGuess we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}事实是我不能为此责怪你俩\NTruth is, I can't blame either of you for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}之前我觉得自己死定了\NHell, there were days there I thought I was a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是当我回来的时候  我回来却面对这一切\NBut when I do come back and what I come back to is this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有时会想这是怎么回事\Nwell, it ain't no great mystery if part of me is thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在这样到底是怎么了\N"What's wrong with this picture?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}唐\NDon--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆  听我说完\NSam, let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道她还爱我\NI know part of her loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在\NAnd now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她也爱你\Npart of her loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是只有艾米利亚自己知道对她来说\NBut the only one that knows what's best for Amelia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最好的选择是什么\Nis Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以当一切说清楚\NSo when all of this is said and done
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她也做出决定时\Nand she's made her decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会尊重她的决定\NI'll respect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你真的爱她  你也会这样做\NAnd if you truly love her, you'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}再给他一杯\NHe could use another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们说什么了\NWhat'd they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们不信  他们去找你了\NThey didn't go for it. They're on their way to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也过去\NI'd get scarce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:22:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无意冒犯  迪恩  可你弟弟\NNo offense, Dean, but your little brother
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可真是吓不了我\Ndoesn't exactly put chills up my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  听我说\NBenny, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别低估我弟弟  好吗\NDo not underestimate my little brother, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有机会的话  他完全可以杀掉你\NHe can and will kill you given the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那现在怎么办\NSo, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去找德斯蒙德\NI go find Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带上我\NYou take me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我刚告诉你\NHey, I just told you --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你最好低调一点\Nbest thing you can do is lay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这回不行  兄弟\NThat ain't gonna work this time, bub.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你带上我  否则我不告诉你他在哪\NYou take me with, or I don't tell you where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道他在哪里吗\NYou know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他说除非我加入他的小巢\NHe said he's not gonna stop the killing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}否则他不会停止杀戮\Ntill I join his little nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}死两个人已经够了\NTwo bodies is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟他说我加入\NI told him I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.42,0:23:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩  这是我的事\NDean, this is my fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你加不加入\NAre you in or are you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么东西把他吓跑了\NSomething spooked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚・理查森\N萨姆  我需要你的帮助  快来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆\NSam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆\NSam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}萨姆\NSam!
