Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我先按兵不动  等你们去\NI hang back while you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喝喝酒确认是否可以相互信任吗\Ndo some trust falls and binge-drinking?
