Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.33,0:25:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会说你还真是瞧不起吸血鬼啊\NI'd say you have an extremely low opinion of us vamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.27,0:25:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这叫有益的怀疑精神\NCall it healthy skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.68,0:26:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼可没告诉我他带了朋友过来\NBenny never told me he was bringing a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.72,0:26:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不会废话太多吧\NYou're not gonna talk a lot, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这一整天\NI've been dealing with crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.11,0:26:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都跟神经病打交道\N...all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.38,0:26:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}混蛋\NSon of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.51,0:26:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可真是慢啊\NIt took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}差一点啊  伙计\NYou've lost a step, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不能再吃那些垃圾食品了\NYou need to lay off the junk food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.61,0:27:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还好吗\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.42,0:27:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没事\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在这里的生活结束了  对吧\NMy life here is over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.73,0:27:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}恐怕是的\NAfraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.80,0:27:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一旦消息走漏出去\NOnce word gets out...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.38,0:27:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那些猎人就会追杀你\N...the machete swingers that'll come for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.88,0:27:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是对付不完的\NYou can't take them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那不可能\NIt's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.98,0:27:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就算你可以\NAnd even if you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们也会有问题\NWe'd have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.88,0:27:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们这样的人  没法定居\NGuys like us, we don't get a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.92,0:27:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也没有家人\NWe don't get family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.34,0:27:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有萨姆\NYou got Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.59,0:28:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.26,0:28:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼  你必须躲起来\NBenny, you got to go deep underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.38,0:28:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}躲到没人知道你身份的地方\Nwhere nobody knows who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.61,0:28:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.91,0:28:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还有最后一件事情要做\NI got one last thing I got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.34,0:28:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}呼叫艾米利亚・理查德森
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.50,0:28:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}您拨打的电话暂时无法接通\NThe person you are trying to reach is unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.63,0:28:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}做什么呢\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.58,0:28:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我\NI'm, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.99,0:28:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我准备走了\NI'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.00,0:28:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.99,0:28:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}唐在酒吧找到你了\NDon found you at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.16,0:28:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚\NAmelia --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.89,0:28:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他威胁你\NHe threatened you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.71,0:29:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚  他没有威胁我\NAmelia, no. He didn't threaten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.87,0:29:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  我只是想做正确的事情\NLook, I'm just trying to do the right thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.90,0:29:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"正确的事"\N"The right thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今早我们俩在一起就是正确的事情  忘了吗\NThis morning, you and I were the right thing, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.21,0:29:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很明白  你和唐需要一次机会\NI know that you and Don deserve a chance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.00,0:29:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你心里也清楚\NAnd...I think you know that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.50,0:29:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给他一次机会吧  你不是也给了我吗\NJust give him a chance -- like you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.02,0:29:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.51,0:29:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚  你拯救了我\NAmelia, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.69,0:29:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}克米特26号公路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.45,0:29:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该走了  老兄\NTime to go, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.04,0:30:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}多谢你没有放弃我  老弟\NThanks for not giving up on me, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.79,0:30:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别给我这样的机会\NDon't give me a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.30,0:30:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}嗨  迪恩\NHey, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我打电话就是要告诉你\NLook, I'm just calling to let you know
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问题已经解决了\Nthat the situation is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.63,0:30:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼没说谎\NBenny was not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.47,0:30:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有一个吸血鬼  我们一起解决了他\NThere was another vamp, and we ganked him -- together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.39,0:30:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很好  迪恩\NOh. That's good, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.07,0:30:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}闭嘴  听我说\NYeah, shut up and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.53,0:30:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼远走高飞了  再也不会回来了\NBenny's long gone, and he won't be coming back ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.91,0:31:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了你好  别再找他了\NSo for your own sake, do not follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.47,0:31:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}明白了吗\NAre we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.75,0:31:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你用不着担心我  迪恩\NYou don't have to worry about me, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.35,0:31:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也远走高飞了\NI'm long gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.42,0:31:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马丁\NOh, and, Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.87,0:31:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}换个行当吧\NFind a new line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.12,0:31:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白来电
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.56,0:31:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}嘿  莉兹\NHey, Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.59,0:31:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}代班情况怎么样\NHow's your shift going?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.30,0:31:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说真的  她代替你干得不错\NI'd say she's covering for you just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.58,0:31:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不过我们这些常客  还是想你\NBut us regulars -- we miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.00,0:31:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是谁\NWho is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.44,0:31:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你应该知道我是谁\NI think you know who this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.02,0:31:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是怎么拿到她手机的\NHow the hell you get her phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.77,0:31:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喜欢吃樱桃酱吗\NYou enjoy the cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.64,0:31:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别动\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.41,0:31:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.11,0:32:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还没吃完呢\NNot quite done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.83,0:32:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}联系上你的朋友了吗\NDid you, uh, reach your friend okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.90,0:32:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  多谢\NI did. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.15,0:32:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不敢相信  我居然把手机掉在巴士上了\NI can't believe I left my cell on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.98,0:32:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}老婆常说我的脑袋要是没拧紧  肯定弄丢了\NWife says I'd lose my own head if it wasn't screwed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.91,0:32:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还要再说一会儿\NI'll just be another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别着急\NWell, you take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.55,0:32:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.86,0:32:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她是个好女孩\NShe's a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.53,0:32:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对陌生人很友好\NTakes kindly to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.64,0:32:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你立刻离她远点\NYou leave her alone -- now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你距离多远\NHow far away are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.82,0:32:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一小时路程\NAn hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.93,0:32:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}给你四十五分钟\NYou got 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.78,0:32:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小姐\NMiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.88,0:32:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的手机\NYour cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.14,0:33:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}胳膊别乱动  邪恶的东西\NLay down your arms, you unholy thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.00,0:33:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我现在来了\NYou got me here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.49,0:33:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不如放了她  让她走\NWhy don't you just let her go and walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.09,0:33:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没这打算\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.97,0:33:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}搞清楚  我可不是求你\NYou realize I'm not asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.91,0:33:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我非常清楚\NI realize that completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.07,0:33:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罗伊  这是怎么回事\NRoy, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.68,0:33:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事  莉兹\NIt's okay, Lizzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.96,0:33:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不会伤害你\NHe ain't gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.79,0:33:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}难道不对吗\NAin't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.18,0:33:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}得了 说吧\NCome on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.82,0:33:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你我之前毫无过节\NI got no beef with you. You got no beef with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.77,0:33:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我跟你这种人可有仇了\NI got plenty of beef with your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.95,0:33:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.13,0:34:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许没错\NThat may be so,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.92,0:34:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是和这里发生的事无关\Nbut not for anything that happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.35,0:34:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没杀那些人\NI did not kill those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.03,0:34:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我听说了\NI heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你和迪恩在炼狱有过交情\NYou and Dean had a little purgatory reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.23,0:34:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真感人\NTouching.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.19,0:34:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罗伊\NRoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.52,0:34:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就告诉我到底出了什么事吧\NPlease just tell me what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.02,0:34:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我求你  别这么做\NI'm asking you -- do not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.83,0:34:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个恶棍已经痛改前非了  好吗\NThe bad guy is gone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.26,0:34:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她不知道\NShe doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.24,0:34:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼\NBenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.15,0:34:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罗伊\NRoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.15,0:34:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}本尼是谁\NWho's Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.69,0:34:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"本尼是谁"\N"Who's Benny"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.52,0:34:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们就弄个真相大白吧  如何\NLet's find out, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.19,0:34:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别过来\NStay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.73,0:34:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.06,0:34:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看见了吗\NSee that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.44,0:34:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}瞳孔扩大\NDilated pupils!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.34,0:34:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}头发直竖\NHair standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.89,0:34:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}饥饿的征兆\NSigns of hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.47,0:35:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别担心\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.68,0:35:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不会吃掉自己的亲骨肉的\NHe won't feed off his own flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.05,0:35:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"亲骨肉"\N"Flesh and blood"?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.67,0:35:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉她啊  本尼\NTell her, Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.92,0:35:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉她你就是她失散多年的爷爷\NTell her how you're her long-lost grandpappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.55,0:35:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉她你欠下了多少条人命\NTell her about all the dead you left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.28,0:35:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉她你是个什么怪物\NTell her about the monster that you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.06,0:35:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想怎么样\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.08,0:35:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还不够清楚吗\NIsn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.20,0:35:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想要你的脑袋\NI want your head on a stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.48,0:36:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罗伊  不要\NRoy, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.33,0:36:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.08,0:36:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}希望他们给你在炼狱\NWell, hope they're saving a special place for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.23,0:36:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}留了个好地方\Nwherever it is you come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.87,0:36:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不要\NNo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.31,0:37:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得今晚还不错\NI feel all right tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喂\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.82,0:37:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迪恩\NDean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.57,0:37:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等一下\NH-hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.41,0:37:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白\NElizabeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.25,0:38:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说要是我看到他  就打给你的\NY-you told me to call you if I saw...him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.69,0:38:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的意思是  看到罗伊了\NWhat do you mean? Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.04,0:38:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他\NIs --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.35,0:38:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他现在就在你旁边\NIs he there right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.53,0:38:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊丽莎白  出什么事了\NElizabeth, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.99,0:38:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快来吧\NJust come.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.64,0:39:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}艾米利亚・理查森\N萨姆  我需要你的帮助  快来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.44,0:40:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}小萨姆\NSammy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.08,0:40:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"萨姆  我需要你的帮助  快来"\N"Sam, I need your help. Come quick."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.27,0:40:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这招不错\NNice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.51,0:40:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}用个火炉就换来了艾米利亚的电话\NSwapping Amelia's phone out with a burner,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}发了求救短信\NSending a distress signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.75,0:40:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你找准了我的死穴\NYou got me good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.31,0:40:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么时候干的\NWhen did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.42,0:40:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有一阵了  以备我不时之需\NWhile back, in case I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.26,0:40:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看来我的决定是对的\NLooks like I made the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.17,0:40:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看见她了吗\NSo, did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.06,0:40:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  我看见她了\NYeah. Yeah, I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.14,0:40:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她挺好的  不过这你也知道\NAnd she's doing just fine. But, 'course, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:40:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其实我并不知道\NActually, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.30,0:40:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只知道这是唯一让你休息的办法\NI did know it was the only way to get you to lay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.94,0:40:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后呢\NSo?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.59,0:40:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}成了吗\NIs it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.06,0:40:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  成了\NYeah, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.10,0:40:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人伤亡吗\NAny casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.44,0:41:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马丁死了\NMartin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.23,0:41:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是本尼吗\NWas it Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.73,0:41:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他自找的  萨姆\NHe had it coming, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.47,0:41:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我告诉你发生什么事了吧\NI'll tell you what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.23,0:41:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道是怎么回事  迪恩\NI-I know what happened, Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还想不想听我说了\NOkay, you want to listen to me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.28,0:41:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}见鬼\NDamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.86,0:41:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道是你\NI knew that was you.

